]]></fr:tex> extends to a function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b^\sharp  \colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x\colon \mathsf {toProp}\,A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}} Bx]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p><fr:p>When we have an element of <fr:tex
